{
  "title": "Rollup 构建配置",
  "description": "学习使用 Rollup 构建 JavaScript 库和应用，掌握 ES 模块打包和 Tree Shaking 优化。",
  "difficulty": "中级",
  "estimatedTime": "25分钟",
  "category": "build-tools",
  "level": 1,
  "objectives": [
    "理解 Rollup 的设计理念和适用场景",
    "配置 Rollup 构建 JavaScript 库",
    "掌握插件系统和代码分割",
    "学习多格式输出配置"
  ],
  "files": [
    {
      "name": "rollup.config.js",
      "type": "config",
      "description": "Rollup 主配置文件"
    },
    {
      "name": "package.json",
      "type": "config", 
      "description": "项目配置和构建脚本"
    },
    {
      "name": "src/index.js",
      "type": "source",
      "description": "库的入口文件"
    },
    {
      "name": "src/utils.js",
      "type": "source",
      "description": "工具函数模块"
    }
  ],
  "validation": {
    "type": "build",
    "commands": ["npm run build"],
    "checkFiles": [
      "dist/index.js",
      "dist/index.esm.js",
      "dist/index.umd.js"
    ]
  },
  "hints": [
    "Rollup 特别适合构建 JavaScript 库",
    "使用 @rollup/plugin-node-resolve 处理 node_modules",
    "配置多种输出格式: ES、CJS、UMD",
    "利用 Tree Shaking 移除未使用的代码"
  ],
  "resources": [
    {
      "title": "Rollup 官方文档",
      "url": "https://rollupjs.org/"
    },
    {
      "title": "Rollup 插件列表",
      "url": "https://github.com/rollup/awesome"
    }
  ]
}